I came into this restaurant tonight because I was dying of hunger! I had never been to this particular location, but I found it along my way to the metro station so I figured why not!  I also had never been to one of these restaurants where both bathrooms were out of order, but it was the case here and it appeared as if someone had passed out, because it was locked tight shut for practically the entire time of my visit.  Finally, a nice Employee was able to unlock one of the bathrooms, which was very helpful!  For dinner, I ordered the steak bowl, which is my usual thing.  It was prepared with some care this time around,, and the steak tasted spicey which was very delicious!  The place was pretty clean clean considering it was Friday, and the music was playing just right, not too loud!  I ended-up eating half of the bowl because I'm calories conscious, and hopefully this weekend I will run-off some of them off!
